{"tid":1419502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！派飯券俾人屈前線有錢收！","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:17:57.000Z","uid":283968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2f753aa42b3bdac87bab46c18013b788f69748","tid":1419502,"uid":283968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"我老母個朋友扭曲晒成個意思！佢話佢琴日係地鐵同兩個着黑衫既妹妹傾計，佢就買咗啲麵包，想分俾妹妹食，跟住個妹妹話唔洗，佢地有飯券，就係書包拎咗出黎，有成疊，過千蚊，我相信個妹妹應該係收集街坊既飯券想派俾前線/有需要既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我老母就收到佢朋友個whatsapp錄音，就扭曲咗妹妹既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話係前線有成千蚊現金券，佢可能理解錯妹妹係前線既人，個妹妹應該係話依千幾蚊現金券派俾有需要既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過派飯券的確幫到好多有需要既人，請同屋企人請清楚，飯券派係有，不過有需要既人先拎，前線手足好多青少年搭車買裝無晒錢食飯，係俾香港政府逼成咁，香港加油！長期戰爭黎！<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，我開設咗條長輩片既Youtube Channel，內容有意義，適合家中長輩睇，教育下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係，後生一輩(小學生)，好需要波子哥哥，一粒屎，灌輸返正確既觀念俾佢地，唔好一味打機開箱，講解下現時情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長輩片頻道連結: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Ffreehongkong&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=1fbfb095\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong</a>"},{"pid":"59de79ba4a56ad953f8fa6223aed666fbe74fc1f","tid":1419502,"uid":283968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:38:25.000Z","msg":"影片:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCnxp7P6SKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcCnxp7P6SKM&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=4e47e8f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCnxp7P6SKM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mh5fSK5TL54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http